rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0001
rows.name:
One of the secrets of Gulan
woodcraft is Puzzletree Wood!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The rings of a Puzzletree's wood form
the shape of a puzzle! Fun to play with
as-is, but also very easy to process!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Here in Gula, we use Puzzletree
Wood for everything from grand houses
to tiny accessories!

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know how we'd get by
without the stuff.

rows.label: tlk41400021_02_msg0005
rows.name:
You can gather Puzzletree Wood from
a lot of the trees round here, so try
collecting it. It might come in handy!
